                            <comment id="13171633" author="markt" created="Sat, 17 Dec 2011 18:35:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The evictor is now stopped before closing the pool.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Marking the pool as closed while the evictor is running won&apos;t cause any harm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Calling clear() in close should cause the evict() method it exit and the evictor thread to terminate as there will no no idle objects to evict.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
